@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
[*] --> Active
Active --> Delivered : submit
Active : entry / log withdrawal
Delivered --> Rejected : confirm
Delivered : entry / log withdrawal
Rejected --> OnHold : update
OnHold --> Closed : approve
OnHold : entry / log withdrawal
Delivered --> OnHold : revert
Closed --> [*]
@enduml